endpoints.name: TIME_SERIES_MONTHLY
endpoints.description: This API returns monthly time series (last trading day of each month, monthly open, monthly high, monthly low, monthly close, monthly volume) of the global equity specified, covering 20+ years of historical data.

endpoints.name: TIME_SERIES_INTRADAY
endpoints.description: This API returns intraday time series (timestamp, open, high, low, close, volume) of the equity specified.

endpoints.name: Quote Endpoint
endpoints.description: A lightweight alternative to the time series APIs, this service returns the price and volume information for a security of your choice.
